flowchart TD
    A([Start Training]) --> B[Initialise Environment\nHTDEEnv: num_tasks, num_executors,\ncomplexity, max_steps]
    B --> C[Initialise Agents\nPPO: PolicyNet per executor\nMADDPG: Actor+Critic per executor]
    C --> D[Initialise Buffer\nPPO: rollout dict\nMADDPG: ReplayBuffer capacity=50000]

    D --> E[Episode Start\nenv.reset\ngenerate new TaskGraph]

    E --> F[Collect Observation\nplanner: full graph\nexecutors: local view]

    F --> G{Algorithm?}

    G -->|PPO| H[Action Selection\nPolicyNet forward pass\nApply action mask\nSample from Categorical dist]
    G -->|MADDPG| I[Action Selection\nActor forward pass\nApply availability mask\nAdd Gumbel noise for exploration\nAnneal noise over training]

    H --> J[Execute Actions\nenv.step actions]
    I --> J

    J --> K[Compute Rewards\nreward_shaping.compute_rewards\nR_global + R_local + R_coord + R_efficiency]
    K --> L[Store Transition\nPPO: append to rollout\nMADDPG: push to ReplayBuffer]

    L --> M{Update condition?}
    M -->|PPO: rollout_len reached| N[PPO Update\nCompute discounted returns\nNormalise advantages\nK epochs clipped surrogate loss\nValue loss + entropy bonus]
    M -->|MADDPG: warmup done\nand every update_every steps| O[MADDPG Update\nSample batch from ReplayBuffer\nUpdate centralised critic MSE loss\nUpdate decentralised actor\nSoft update target networks tau=0.005]
    M -->|Not yet| P{Episode done?}
    N --> P
    O --> P

    P -->|No| F
    P -->|Yes| Q[Log episode reward\nCheck convergence]

    Q --> R{Max episodes\nreached?}
    R -->|No| E
    R -->|Yes| S[Evaluate\nrun_eval 50 greedy episodes\ncompute_metrics]
    S --> T([End Training\nSave results + plots])
